definitions.definition: Picked when small and immature (as in baby corn , baby potatoes ).
Newest (overall, or in some group or state); most inexperienced .
Like or pertaining to a baby , in size or youth; small, young.

main_definition: ( of vegetables, etc. ) Picked when small and immature (as in baby corn , baby potatoes ).
secondary_definitions: Newest (overall, or in some group or state); most inexperienced .
( in the comparative or superlative ) Like or pertaining to a baby , in size or youth; small, young.
